rows.label: qev025306_MSG0001
rows.name: Hey there! Welcome to the Sunshine Café![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025306_MSG0002
rows.name:
What's that? You need an iconic New LA food?
Well, you've come to the right place, because there's
nothing more iconic than our famous Sunny Dog![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025306_MSG0003
rows.name:
It's a spicy hot dog with the works, guaranteed to stay
molten-lava hot from the first bite to the last. And talk
about a bargain—this bad boy's only 600 credits![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025306_SEL0011
rows.name: Purchase a hot dog for 600 credits.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025306_MSG0004
rows.name:
Order UP! ...Yeah, don't worry—this baby will rock the
pants off your xeno buddy. Assuming he wears pants.
Oh, and it's super hot, so be careful carrying it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025306_MSG0005
rows.name:
You sure? They're kind of amazing.
Well, we'll be here if you change your mind.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025306_MSG0006
rows.name: Um, is this all the money you have?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025306_MSG0007
rows.name:
Yeah, sorry. You don't have enough to buy a hot dog.
Which is...kinda sad.[ST:wait ]
